Package com.github.westonpace.jayvee.workflow

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Sink<T>
    A data sink that items are pushed into.
    Source<T>
    A source that data can be 'pop'ed from.
    Worker
    An object that can be iterated to process data from sources into sinks.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DirectCallBuffer<T>
    A buffer which can be used for OnRequestOnly workers.
    StandardWorker
    A standard worker implementation which provides logic for signalling when a worker has ended.
    SystemBuilder
    A programmatic interface for building systems and subsystems.
    WorkflowSystem
    Controller for a collection of workers.
    WorklessWorkerRunnable  
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    BufferEndedException
    An exception thrown when trying to access a buffer that someone has already called end on (and all other items have emptied out)
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    InputBuffer
    A marker used to indicate that a particular field or property is an input Source to a worker or system.
    OnRequestOnly  
    OutputBuffer
    A marker used to indicate that a particular field or property is an output Sink to a worker or system.
